<HISTITEMS>
<HISTITEM authorref='_00000230E75DE420' stid='0' tool='CANdelaStudio 8.2 Beta 2  Admin' dt='2015-06-30 12:45:45+02:00'>
<LABEL>1.0</LABEL>
<MOD>Created</MOD>
<REASON>Adapt Example Templates (EIP32668)
based on project EIP25954.</REASON>
</HISTITEM>
<HISTITEM authorref='_00000230E75DE420' stid='0' tool='CANdelaStudio 8.2 Beta 3  Admin' dt='2015-07-13 12:30:14+02:00'>
<LABEL>1.0.1</LABEL>
<MOD>In Download diagnostic class template, separated "FormatIdentifier" of request and positive response in service "0x34 Request" </MOD>
<REASON>The data have different semantics:
- request: "dataFormatIdentifier"
- response "lengthFormatIdentifier"
(EIP32957)</REASON>
</HISTITEM>
<HISTITEM authorref='_00000230E75DE420' stid='0' tool='CANdelaStudio 8.2 Beta 3  Admin' dt='2015-07-15 09:29:27+02:00'>
<LABEL>1.0.2</LABEL>
<MOD>Added Snapshot Record "Last Occurrence" and some DIDs in Snapshot Data, also in Common Diagnostics for 2 specific DTCs.
Adapted Protocol Services 0x23, 0x34, 0x35, 0x3D: put Multiplexer into fixed data.
Adapted Protocol Service 0x85: added Options.</MOD>
<REASON>More example Snapshot Data.
Avoid editing of memory address and size in diagnostic instances.
Support optional Control Options Record of 0x85.</REASON>
</HISTITEM>
<HISTITEM authorref='_00000230E75DE420' stid='0' tool='Emacs' dt='2015-11-19 14:40:00+01:00'>
<LABEL>1.0.3</LABEL>
<MOD>Brake Pressure must contain DID Data Reference instead of DID Reference.</MOD>
<REASON>A diagnostic instance describes the identifier by itself, not included in the reference.</REASON>
</HISTITEM>
<HISTITEM authorref='_00000230E75DE420' stid='0' tool='Emacs' dt='2016-03-07 13:19:27+01:00'>
<LABEL>1.0.4</LABEL>
<MOD>Shorten qualifier of 19 06 Protocol Service</MOD>
<REASON>It exceeded the 64 character limit defined in the document.</REASON>
</HISTITEM>
<HISTITEM authorref='_00000230E75DE420' stid='0' tool='Emacs' dt='2016-06-02 08:48:00+01:00'>
<LABEL>1.1</LABEL>
<MOD>Rename variants from "Development" etc. to "A Sample" etc.
Now based on UDS 2013 (no change of contents).</MOD>
<REASON>"Development", "Production" and "After Sales" is not typically reflected in different variants.</REASON>
</HISTITEM>
<HISTITEM authorref='_00000230E75DE420' stid='0' tool='Emacs' dt='2016-07-04 07:38:00+01:00'>
<LABEL>1.1.01</LABEL>
<MOD>Removed 1 leading and 9 trailing blanks in names and descriptions.</MOD>
<REASON>Avoid irritating behavior with names erroneously supposed to be duplicate.</REASON>
</HISTITEM>
<HISTITEM authorref='_00000230E75DE420' stid='1' tool='CANdelaStudio 9.1 Release Admin' dt='2018-01-23 15:18:30+01:00'>
<LABEL>1.2</LABEL>
<MOD>Deleted duplicate data types with final "(1)"</MOD>
<REASON>The data types are not needed.</REASON>
</HISTITEM>
<HISTITEM authorref='_00000230E75DE420' stid='1' tool='CANdelaStudio 10 ReleasePatch 2  Admin' dt='2018-08-14 13:43:08+02:00'>
<LABEL>1.3</LABEL>
<MOD>Checked File | Properties | "Document Info" | "Attributes for AUTOSAR Diagnostic Extract export"</MOD>
<REASON>Make document usable for AUTOSAR process operations</REASON>
</HISTITEM>
</HISTITEMS>
